text: Lia Beel Quintana (born 22 July 1995 in Pinjarra, Australia) is a blind Spanish Paralympic athlete who competes in sprinting events in international level events. She trains with her husband David Alonso Gutierrez who is her running guide. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:People from Toledo, Spain Category:Paralympic athletes of Spain Category:Spanish female sprinters Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Paralympics
